Filmed in and around the chicagoland area, and also in northwestern Indiana, WhackPak take you along for a ride with some of the best freestyle street riders there are. You'll see plenty of crashes, 12 o'clock wheelies, long endos, and no-handers. This video features the riding of Aaron Pepowski and has special appearances by Thew Blankstrom and Matt Gorka of Team1096, Matt Weber and Jeremy Bonk of I.B.W.S., and also Todd Colbert.
